{
  "stem": "12343.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 593.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said to my mother, why you have to learn-- [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He broke my heart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let him go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to teach him about tailor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I started to go to for a tailor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all the time, they used to ask me, the boys, my friend, why you come back to school?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you come back this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, tomorrow, tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's happening.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never got back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How old were you when you started to learn how to be a tailor?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "13 years old.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I remember-- not good-- not very good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is there to remember?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I never want to remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't like to remember any more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I suffer a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING] See, that is all I think, [INAUDIBLE] before, cause I got nothing [INAUDIBLE] it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I get, you know, older, and started to work and learn a trade, and I started to make money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then my-- then I said to my mother and it broke her heart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my sister started to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She used to make bras-- how you call it-- for-- for a woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Very good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she started to work, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then, that is happen the trouble.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And comes the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my mother used to-- religious-- we-- we are Jews and religious, very religious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, she never said [INAUDIBLE] Saturdays, you cannot do it Fridays, Saturdays, not in Europe, difference.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- first of all, they never had electric over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How you call it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Gas-- night-- different lamps, you know, you have to in, not gasoline.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How you call it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kerosene.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that's always life in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, when I started to work, it was different, all different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Changed then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not for a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
